To create a client ID and client secret
go to https://console.developers.google.com

Create new project, enter a project name (such as "GDrive Sync").
After a project is created, click the project name to open its properties.

From left menu select "APIs & auth", "APIs".
Select Drive API from APIs list and turn it on

Now select "Credentials" from left menu
Press "create new Client ID"
In the Client ID Settings section, do the following:
Select Installed application for the Application type.
Select Other Installed application type.
Download json file and copy it to ./secrets folder.
